    <briefdescription>
<para>\par \b Purpose\/ \:  Hold information about files attached to the parsed document: original name, disk path, content analysis flag, and UID. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Holds information about files, attached to the parsed document.</para>
<para>:ivar original_name: original name of the attached file if it was possible to extract it :ivar tmp_file_path: path to the attached file on disk - its name is different from original_name :ivar need_content_analysis: does the attached file need parsing (enable recursive parsing in :class:<computeroutput>~dedoc.DedocManager</computeroutput>) :ivar uid: unique identifier of the attached file</para>
<para>:vartype original_name: str :vartype tmp_file_path: str :vartype need_content_analysis: bool :vartype uid: str </para>
    </detaileddescription>
